header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: Florida State's Phil Cofer finds Terance Mann for the transition dunk early against Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Nice dish sets up dunk for FSU

videos.description: Matt Farrell makes the corner 3-pointer on the inbound play as Notre Dame extends their lead over FSU.
videos.headline: Notre Dame shooting lights out from beyond the arc

videos.description: Notre Dame's Steve Vasturia makes the 3-pointer before accidentally getting hit in the mouth by his teammate, Austin Torres, while running back on defense.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Vasturia take shot from teammate after bucket

videos.description: Matt Farrell finds Bonzie Colson in transition for the layup followed by Matt Ryan driving along the baseline for a layup as Notre Dame extends their lead over FSU.
videos.headline: Notre Dame taking control in first half

videos.description: Matt Farrell makes one of his team's eight 3-pointers in the first half to help give Notre Dame the commanding halftime lead over FSU.
videos.headline: No luck needed for Irish in first half

videos.description: Notre Dame coach Mike Brey talks about staying hungry and in rhythm in the second half against FSU.
videos.headline: Brey proud of team's effort in first half

videos.description: Steve Vasturia uses the ball fake to get free from the defense before dishing to Bonzie Colson for the easy bucket.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Vasturia gets defender to bite

videos.description: Matt Ryan makes the corner 3-pointer as Notre Dame extends their lead over FSU.
videos.headline: Notre Dame continues to fire from deep

videos.description: FUS's Christ Koumadje blocks the pass, causing the ball to bounce off the face of Notre Dame's Matt Farrell and giving possession to the Seminoles.
videos.headline: Matt Farrell takes block off the face, causes Notre Dame turnover

videos.description: Steve Vasturia makes the 3-pointer for Notre Dame and then Braian Angola-Rodas answers with a 3-pointer of his own for FSU.
videos.headline: Irish, Seminoles trading buckets in second half
